{"tid":669963,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"表面上我係個地產狗，其實我係黑社會","createTime":"2018-05-19T02:39:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T14:54:36.000Z","uid":90605,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"37285a5d8d902b0490a81a3ea543df1583caf712","tid":669963,"uid":90605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T02:39:01.000Z","msg":"地產狗，日日做黎做去都要得雞碎咁多人工，又要隻揪爭客，爭到又比師兄食住佣金。<br />\n<br />\n我係一個黑社會大佬，由大學grad開始，我就跟我老豆搵食，其實我老豆係黑社會揸fit人，由細開始，我成日見佢打到傷哂，佢供我讀大學就係想我幫佢管理社團。<br />\n<br />\n點知有一次我出街比一班Mk西裝友捉左我去睇樓，我話唔睇樓，佢話我大佬要見你，之後我上到去，有條友個樣好似三哥既人叫我入去傾！"},{"pid":"a96abac6cfd305fc7e50e4b91ea9e24ac3a91019","tid":669963,"uid":164991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T02:40:39.000Z","msg":"不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75d70245a03b01ff4a40e051c5dcb28250508c4","tid":669963,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T02:41:45.000Z","msg":"巴打，比幾分鐘時間你，帶番個頭盔"},{"pid":"c4d18237ced417e8dab280be4035abc1f2aff5fc","tid":669963,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T02:51:17.000Z","msg":"社團條例 151 20<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ed816f39443fa19081f5310fa252ceaf074111","tid":669963,"uid":48605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c75d70245a03b01ff4a40e051c5dcb28250508c4","tid":669963,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T02:41:45.000Z","msg":"巴打，比幾分鐘時間你，帶番個頭盔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:04:35.000Z","msg":"告得入個的士佬都比人捉左啦"},{"pid":"66bf5697494c4a0905685c04c9f4b559ec2033d9","tid":669963,"uid":90605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T14:36:34.000Z","msg":"入到去：條友話：「最近你老豆有咩吩咐我？<br />\n老豆叫我同你做一隻地產狗經理，然後利用地產狗經理身份幫你老豆找錢，係咁多！<br />\n未正式介紹：我叫DogDog，你可以叫我狗公公<br />\nHi，狗公公<br />\n之後我就同狗公公兩條友開左間搶錢地產<br />\n入面得我同佢，準備請多幾條友返黎"},{"pid":"e0c04955d47909b8b2949dad3673db27a8cb78dd","tid":669963,"uid":126029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T14:54:36.000Z","msg":"樓主話係黑社會好似冇犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}